<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Owner History – Cx6</title>

  <style>
    body {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #050505, #000000 80%);
      color: #d9d9d9;
      font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #8a2be2;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px #8a2be2, 0 0 25px #4b0082;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.95);
      border: 1px solid #8a2be2;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 15px #8a2be233,
        inset 0 0 10px #8a2be222;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 1em;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #c77dff;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-shadow: 0 0 6px #c77dff;
    }

    .accent {
      color: #00f0ff;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-shadow: 0 0 6px #00f0ff;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #8a2be2, transparent);
      margin: 20px 0;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        padding: 10px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 0.95em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <h1>OWNER HISTORY — CX6</h1>

  <div class="container">

    <p>
      My journey began in <span class="highlight">2024</span> when I joined 
      <span class="accent">Slayers of Destiny</span>. Through 
      <span class="highlight">consistency</span> and 
      <span class="highlight">discipline</span>, I rose to 
      <span class="accent">Leader Moderator</span>, securing a key role within the clan.
    </p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <p>
      After the split, I became the owner of 
      <span class="accent">PO</span>, leading during a time of 
      <span class="highlight">instability</span>. An alliance with 
      <span class="accent">GA</span> was formed to maintain balance — but as tensions grew, it collapsed, turning 
      <span class="accent">GA</span> into a rival force.
    </p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <p>
      This era forged my <span class="highlight">leadership</span>, strengthening my ability to 
      <span class="highlight">manage conflict</span>, 
      <span class="highlight">adapt under pressure</span>, and 
      <span class="highlight">lead with control</span> in competitive environments.
    </p>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
